Alembic migrations for AI-Cyber-Defense-Network.

This project uses:
- SQLAlchemy 2.x models
- Metadata imported from app.db.base.Base
- Dynamic database URL from app.core.config.settings.database_url

Workflow:
1) Define/update models in app/db/models/
2) Generate migration with: alembic revision --autogenerate -m "..."
3) Apply with: alembic upgrade head
4) Verify downgrade with: alembic downgrade -1 (or to base)

